3.label: 3. N-benzylbenzamide
3.description:
Synthesised according to the general procedure, using 5 mol% or 2 mol% catalyst loading. Purified by flash column chromatography (EtOAc:Cyclohexane 30% à 60%). Analytical data in accordance with literature reports.5 Yield = 923 mg white solid, 4.37 mmol, 87%
1H NMR (700 MHz, CDCl3): δ (ppm) = 7.79 (d, J = 7.6 Hz, 2H), 7.50 (t, J = 7.3 Hz, 1H), 7.43 (t, J = 7.6 Hz, 2H), 7.36 (m, 4H), 7.33-7.28 (m, 1H), 6.46 (s, 1H), 4.65 (d, J = 5.6 Hz, 2H).
13C NMR (176 MHz, CDCl3): δ (ppm) = 167.48, 138.31, 134.52, 131.70, 128.94, 128.74, 128.07, 127.78, 127.09, 44.28.
HRMS [C14H13NO+H]+ Expected 212.1081 Observed 212.1068
Melting point: 92-93 °C
